class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7512092d931b17a983e8475a3eaad0cce45068b8","tid":81580,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T22:37:50.000Z","msg":"你個名點讀"},{"pid":"b69f7a3c9a7351c81b41f913cdc3381bf3af7030","tid":81580,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T23:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生喺頭唔會好怪咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/R74DOs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FR74DOs.png&h=11fb1bd3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9614da36ea65d377fe728f1b0fdfb7f6b1144b6","tid":81580,"uid":70538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T23:25:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>生喺頭唔會好怪咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/R74DOs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FR74DOs.png&h=11fb1bd3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n銀魂"},{"pid":"9322a3ca44958b849f1bb43f14c8f449b42b7763","tid":81580,"uid":70538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T23:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天生囉 成班傻鳩係到諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔好問隻眼點解生係頭到？</blockquote><br />\n上面咪問撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點解天生要係兩腿之間?<br />\n如果你天生係指隨機，咁點解定左係兩腿之間就冇再變過?<br />\n<br />\nbtw， 我估你個腦天生就生錯位"},{"pid":"5347a5b7f8171cb497c3c59617989b18e9bbadb8","tid":81580,"uid":57790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T23:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你唔撚好問下點解所有動物隻眼都生係個頭到<br />\n都on撚鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解所有動物隻眼都生係頭到？</blockquote><br />\n點解所有動物個鼻都生係頭到？</blockquote><br />\n點解所有動物個口都生係頭到？</blockquote><br />\n眼耳口鼻都係特別感覺器官，神經系統比身體其它部位易受傷同複雜，所以集中係個頭到，一黎保護好d(頭骨硬)，二黎可以集中d特別神經線，令線路有效率d(一條腦神經會比幾個感覺器官共用)"},{"pid":"23429aa6a4fe6dad75897d787d80f14f31f3d451","tid":81580,"uid":46862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T00:14:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161220/1016315/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20161220%2F1016315%2F&d=eglcHZo5bQlIHxwLRU4D2ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=de804359\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161220/1016315/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7d3d4fadef72fe06929eabe27042347422b64d","tid":81580,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T00:36:34.000Z","msg":"軟體類就唔係啦<br />\n乜野全部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無睇過蝸牛交配<br />\n佢地真係格劍鬥邊個插贏<br />\n輸左就做0仔<br />\n贏左就去搵下個目標<br />\n而且正確d講好多都係身體正下方<br />\n睪丸係魚類等非溫血動物係正下方<br />\n人類胚胎時睪丸就係肚上面係祖先所在位置<br />\n胚胎發展時會慢慢移落去下面<br />\n人類有胃腸氣係因為睪丸移動後引起<br />\n下面篇文有講<br />\n<a href=\"http://sa.ylib.com/MagArticle.aspx?Unit=featurearticles&amp;id=1343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsa.ylib.com%2FMagArticle.aspx%3FUnit%3Dfeaturearticles%26id%3D1343&d=eglcHZo5bQlIHxwLRU4D2ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=63116993\" target=\"_blank\">http://sa.ylib.com/MagArticle.aspx?Unit=featurearticles&amp;id=1343</a>"},{"pid":"0e97c91c035351d641ec8bab172b646d801c7c0f","tid":81580,"uid":21325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:00:56.000Z","msg":"高汁post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd579a32fe5c9ba46c657534afec968a1150f60","tid":81580,"uid":4256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:06:25.000Z","msg":"到底邊個決定d位置"},{"pid":"57f3f755183c7c74d2d1b89789619edee7455b16","tid":81580,"uid":67824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:10:11.000Z","msg":"因為可以等大家可以交換動類都識交配，因為知道個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbd0dc50f2c45278133c6fa23ccb0cb64bf4e54","tid":81580,"uid":63870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:14:43.000Z","msg":"唔記得公定母既刺猬，性器官係生係心口"},{"pid":"8e6a1a57f0b0c19225d4cf4390ddbaef50bd7b7f","tid":81580,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:34:35.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}